snippet.title: Growtopia Teaser 2: Soulmates
snippet.description:
Growtopia is a new new experimental multiplayer creative sandbox platformer mmo from Seth A. Robinson and Mike Hommel coming to a mobile system near you Jan 11th!  Try saying that fast a few times.

Free to play, with in-app currency purchase. Currency can be earned through gameplay as well, for truly free play..

Credit:

"About" from the Growtopia OST  by Cory Mollenhour ( cory.mollenhour.com/music.html )

"Danse Morialta" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)

Special thanks to Mike Kasprzak and Phil Hassey for their incredible acting skills
